  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your broiler.",
    "Mix bread crumbs with olive oil, orange zest, orange juice, sesame seeds, and garlic powder until well combined. The mixture should be slightly wet.",
    "Spread the redcurrants in a single layer on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Press the breadcrumb mixture onto each redcurrant half, ensuring they are evenly coated.",
    "Place under the preheated broiler for 2-3 minutes or until golden brown. Watch carefully to avoid burning.",
    "Remove from heat and serve immediately."
  ],
